":"83daef083deac9f93da704b8aae58f0c71bcfcaf","tid":510631,"uid":22349,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"有好轉，未好翻，好反覆<br />\n<br />\n好多人以為我唔開心得情緒好波動，好唔冷靜。<br />\n<br />\n其實依刻我唔開心得好平靜，無波動<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係一條處於低位既水平線，很平靜<br />\n<br />\n亦似一潭死水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T18:17:40.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"8918f4a3805f05aa9b5c668db128e1434a1059a8","tid":510631,"uid":160175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T18:18:32.000Z","msg":"14年個時有過，成日行行下街喊，每日都好怕訓醒個一刻，一脫離睡眠、脫離夢境就覺得好絕望，睇左幾次醫生就冇再睇，因為個心好清楚只可以自救。後尾有好翻好多，但上年又有一段時間翻發，好想死，成日等roommate訓著就自己偷偷地喊。總之每隔一段時間就會莫名低位，我好努力控制住自己唔好咁，唔好諗，因為我想為係低谷拯救過我既人好好生存，但都係盡力啦，有時真係控制唔到。<br />\n<br />\nBtw 樓上用一潭死水黎形容真係好貼切"},{"pid":"16751f66107dbcfcfd8923e10c9a2872b4d5b2eb","tid":510631,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c58fe64d8af861262d63327d2f3c1f133d67ac1d","tid":510631,"uid":178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T18:12:09.000Z","msg":"冇好返<br />\n一係搵野做到麻木，一係長時間跌到去谷底麻木，但都會好易俾小事搞到病發"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T18:19:53.000Z","msg":"一有咩小事就好易黎料"},{"pid":"0ad33b9b58e63239828e2126a9ff71fa963d0164","tid":510631,"uid":22349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T18:24:40.000Z","msg":"無諗過控制到，同佢共存已經係最好既狀況"},{"pid":"ab8740cac8dd0c329096709d1152d3fa2185c23b","tid":510631,"uid":148884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T18:36:30.000Z","msg":"想知各位係睇咩醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n政府又好似好hea<br />\n私家又太貴<br />\n藥又唔敢食<br />\n<br />\n以前情緒好波動<br />\n而家變到無感覺無快樂乜都唔想做"},{"pid":"709449629a04eba06d8d32eaf92f01bfda9e40e7","tid":510631,"uid":126615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T19:10:01.000Z","msg":"我咁多年冇去睇過醫生 冇正式確診過 但懷疑自己有depression <br />\n其實呢個病真係唔會走 中一中二嗰陣最低潮自己介手自殘<br />\n到到後尾靠自己先挨得住 等自己唔好諗負面野<br />\n但呢一年黎遇到嘅唔開心野又一連串咁trigger番以前嘅野 然後而家又有自殘自殺念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..."},{"pid":"ad07c4012b3cd1fb24d9294d558c10e7e624ed27","tid":510631,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T19:15:00.000Z","msg":"除左睇醫生<br />\n仲有咩方法知自己有冇抑鬱症"},{"pid":"5cb6eabc679bf14a2ca4d21593d6d6e2b38014d1","tid":510631,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T19:48:34.000Z","msg":"如果呢個病係一個人，我一定會打撚死佢，打到佢仆街冚家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但可惜呢一刻係我俾佢㩒住黎打，每次個種絕望嘅感覺一到，我就會係心入面講 : 又黎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一潭死水，無事咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有事嗰陣你個人想靜都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46bd0b92328c9508549e43dba94dd2e2e0e34921","tid":510631,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68ebd2e04eabe7d936145453cbcfabc06b2e3f3f","tid":510631,"uid":148857,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T17:38:13.000Z","msg":"我覺得食藥只係令你對事物既感覺好似矇上一層保鮮紙，唔會太波動到你既情緒，但可唔可以令你好番？個人經驗覺得麻麻。始終都係要靠自己，逼自己諗野正面，逼自己求變，咁先有出路，咁先會好啲。一直縱容自己沉溺係負面情緒，一定唔會好。<br />\n<br />\n利申：食左一個月藥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T19:50:17.000Z","msg":"食左成年"},{"pid":"0db4e3a2b39fe9d1197cd0bc28fd9fa3e66f7b1a","tid":510631,"uid":127755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T20:01:46.000Z","msg":"如果屋企人有，點先幫到佢，佢食左好多年藥都冇咩好轉，仲好似差左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好想佢好番"},{"pid":"5d29c3e7b1256009d205945acc2f30a1ed52dd7a","tid":510631,"uid":41477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad07c4012b3cd1fb24d9294d558c10e7e624ed27","tid":510631,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T19:15:00.000Z","msg":"除左睇醫生<br />\n仲有咩方法知自己有冇抑鬱症"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T02:21:48.000Z","msg":"小小鬱躁症自我評估：<br />\n<br />\n1. 成日都好倦，除左唔願出街。<br />\n2. 無緣故地暴躁，發脾氣，事後想番會後悔。<br />\n3. 聽人講野會覺得受到針對，小小事都會刺激到自己。<br />\n<br />\n當然仲有好多情況，例如溝埋強迫症和驚恐症既時候。"},{"pid":"5b9db0943c62e6c2b381e94607c50d3d7e2640e1","tid":510631,"uid":68813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ad33b9b58e63239828e2126a9ff71fa963d0164","tid":510631,"uid":22349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T18:24:40.000Z","msg":"無諗過控制到，同佢共存已經係最好既狀況"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T02:54:01.000Z","msg":"你呢句都好大既反思<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce528d4a68de4b208c5e446323421403dd40d92d","tid":510631,"uid":68813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cb6eabc679bf14a2ca4d21593d6d6e2b38014d1","tid":510631,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T19:48:34.000Z","msg":"如果呢個病係一個人，我一定會打撚死佢，打到佢仆街冚家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但可惜呢一刻係我俾佢㩒住黎打，每次個種絕望嘅感覺一到，我就會係心入面講 : 又黎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一潭死水，無事咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有事嗰陣你個人想靜都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T02:55:41.000Z","msg":"想知，佢來個下係咩感覺架"},{"pid":"98f2e3825931adf3e072f1bd75b8ea7d36987e64","tid":510631,"uid":54597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:38:55.000Z","msg":"絕症黎<br />\n打理自己情緒同做gym 一樣，係終身事業"},{"pid":"93b99fc56af4ac5d5f899c3521222018a240180a","tid":510631,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T04:01:43.000Z","msg":"其實會醞釀幾耐先會有？無知一問"},{"pid":"b1e2d88ab5b21e154349d127764c00f1bb4915f7","tid":510631,"uid":131372,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T04:12:28.000Z","msg":"Here<br />\n唔知算唔算好反，以前會失去哂所有興趣，無啦啦唔開心，覺得自己好廢，唔想去離其他人，個人無情感咁。宜家已經無乜呢啲感覺，就算有都會好快無事，<br />\n原本有睇過心理醫生，但覺得無乜用最未都無睇，上網睇左一個叫Elliott hulse嘅channel,呢個人之前都係有試過depression。佢話depression 係因為人唔去express自己，應該去做多啲運動等身體運動多啲，想反你用個腦去諗唔會䆁放到呢啲負面能量，應該比自己個腦休息下。佢仲有好多好多關於呢樣嘢嘅意見。最緊要自己要肯幫自己。加油加油"},{"pid":"d6570e3ee705c95cc7547754dbe0c0b411943803","tid":510631,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T12:35:26.000Z","msg":"個個中二病都覺得自己抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n真抑鬱應該唔會有心情吹水?"},{"pid":"f153ef6d03872f84cf23fd8cfef610f77e0e1907","tid":510631,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce528d4a68de4b208c5e446323421403dd40d92d","tid":510631,"uid":68813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cb6eabc679bf14a2ca4d21593d6d6e2b38014d1","tid":510631,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T19:48:34.000Z","msg":"如果呢個病係一個人，我一定會打撚死佢，打到佢仆街冚家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但可惜呢一刻係我俾佢㩒住黎打，每次個種絕望嘅感覺一到，我就會係心入面講 : 又黎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一潭死水，無事咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有事嗰陣你個人想靜都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T02:55:41.000Z","msg":"想知，佢來個下係咩感覺架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:32:56.000Z","msg":"睇乜都好絕望、煩躁，唔想面對個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc92b32a0bca27c9b30aac17dd86b694b532c05","tid":510631,"uid":21260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:26:03.000Z","msg":"想問下<br />\n最想人同你講咩<br />\n同埋最唔想人同你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c8376b670d3105791b89a9ed01082a009cf3e8","tid":510631,"uid":164419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:29:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"441bef373461531ff6ae9625e42c259ff0ee2522","tid":510631,"uid":75025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:34:47.000Z","msg":"要每日都諗下d 正面野<br />\n例如每日寫3件開心既事<br />\n去欣賞多d呢個世界"},{"pid":"dc23634ce807de2bac1f6bc66ea81d3755efc28d","tid":510631,"uid":73366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:35:12.000Z","msg":"唔洗諗咁多係咪一世都唔會好，其實就好似傷風感冒咁，好返之後又係一條好漢，但成世人都有機會隨時復發，平時無事既時候咪做多啲運動，俾多啲抵抗力自己，唔好俾自己咁易復發，到真係再有事，都會易處理啲。"},{"pid":"f38f6310c536d780196b90c29cc0d6973209c118","tid":510631,"uid":3581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:13:03.000Z","msg":"轉哂成個環境, 重新開始<br />\n<br />\n食返野, 跟住都唔知點解就冇事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3944fcd4119466ba788fbbfd1aa9ad4a61d1fa","tid":510631,"uid":114275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:29:43.000Z","msg":"認真你 keep 住睇連登呢 d 討論區好易複發架喎<br />\n<br />\n唔抑鬱都睇到抑鬱啦 ..."},{"pid":"f11ed0d913ad8d0ffc79f232bc02d6a7a0127ea9","tid":510631,"uid":68813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f153ef6d03872f84cf23fd8cfef610f77e0e1907","tid":510631,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce528d4a68de4b208c5e446323421403dd40d92d","tid":510631,"uid":68813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cb6eabc679bf14a2ca4d21593d6d6e2b38014d1","tid":510631,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T19:48:34.000Z","msg":"如果呢個病係一個人，我一定會打撚死佢，打到佢仆街冚家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但可惜呢一刻係我俾佢㩒住黎打，每次個種絕望嘅感覺一到，我就會係心入面講 : 又黎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一潭死水，無事咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有事嗰陣你個人想靜都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T02:55:41.000Z","msg":"想知，佢來個下係咩感覺架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:32:56.000Z","msg":"睇乜都好絕望、煩躁，唔想面對個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T17:01:04.000Z","msg":"姐係平時個人會正面D架`?"},{"pid":"44738f71cbaf400ff0601545913449f4779f5755","tid":510631,"uid":68813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f3944fcd4119466ba788fbbfd1aa9ad4a61d1fa","